The '''IV [[ALBA Games]]''' (Spanish: ''Juegos del ALBA Bicentenario'') is a [[multi-sport event]] held between 17–30 July 2010 in ten different states of [[Venezuela]].<ref name=Host>{{cite web|title=Todo listo para los IV Juegos del ALBA a realizarse en Venezuela|url=http://www.telesurtv.net/secciones/noticias/95203/todo-listo-para-los-iv-juegos-del-alba-a-realizarse-en-venezuela/|work=[[TeleSUR]]|language=Spanish|accessdate=16 July 2011}}</ref> The games are organized by the [[Bolivarian Alliance for the Americas]] (ALBA).

