'''Karbi Youth Festival''' is an annual festival celebrated by the [[Karbi People]] of Assam. It is celebrated on 15–19 February of every year in Taralangso, [[Diphu]], [[Karbi Anglong District]]. It is locally called '''Riso-Nimso Rong Arje'''.<ref name=Mileage>{{cite web|title=Karbi Youth Festival, 2015|url=http://themileage.org/2015/03/karbi-youth-festival-2015.html|publisher=The Mileage|accessdate=20 January 2016|date=3 March 2015}}</ref>

