{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2015}} '''''Reporter''''' is a [[Political journalism|political magazine]] published in [[Slovenia]]. The magazine was first published in May 2008.<ref name=mls>{{cite web|author1=Marko Milosavljević|author2=Igor Vobič|title=Media landscapes. Slovenia|url=http://ejc.net/media_landscapes/slovenia|work=European Journalism Centre|accessdate=29 May 2015}}</ref> The editors of the magazine are mostly former contributors of now-defunct Slovene magazine, ''[[Mag (Slovenian magazine)|Mag]]''.<ref name=mls/> ''Reporter'' is published on a weekly basis.<ref>{{cite book|author1=David H. Weaver|author2=Lars Willnat|title=The Global Journalist in the 21st Century|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ETE5vVTeLQkC&pg=PA284|accessdate=29 May 2015|year=2012|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-0-415-88576-8|page=284}}</ref> The magazine has a rightist political stance<ref name=mls/> and has an ideological connection with the [[right-wing]] [[Slovenian Democratic Party]].<ref>{{cite book|author1=Tamara Caraus|author2=Camil Alexandru Parvu|title=Cosmopolitanism and the Legacies of Dissent|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fG0KBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA59|accessdate=29 May 2015|date=17 July 2014|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-317-64502-3|page=59}}</ref>
