{{Infobox music festival | name =Resistanz Festival | image =Resistanz 2014.jpg | caption =Held in 2014 | location =[[Sheffield, United Kingdom]] | years_active =2011-2016 | founders = | dates = | genre = [[Industrial music]] | attendance = | capacity = | website =[http://www.corporation.org.uk/resistanzfestival/ Official Website] }} '''Resistanz''' was an [[industrial music]] [[music festival|festival]] held annually from 2011 until 2016 over the [[Easter]] weekend, at the [[Corporation (nightclub)|Corporation]] [[music venue|venue]] in [[Sheffield, United Kingdom]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.soundspheremag.com/reviews/live/live-review-resistanz-festival-2011-the-corporation-sheffield/|title=Live Review: Resistanz Festival 2011 [The Corporation, Sheffield]|date=11 April 2011|access-date=22 March 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.soundspheremag.com/reviews/live/resistanz-festival-2012-corp-sheffield/|title=Live Review: Resistanz Festival 2012 [Corporation, Sheffield]|date=19 April 2012|access-date=22 March 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skiddle.com/whats-on/Sheffield/Corporation/Resistanz-Festival/12338807/|title=Resistanz Festival on Fri 3rd April 2015|access-date=22 March 2016}}</ref> The festival primarily featured [[alternative electronic]] music acts including industrial, [[electronic body music|EBM]], [[futurepop]], [[synthpop]] and [[power noise]]. In later years the festival expanded to include a smaller second room featuring an eclectic mix of artists from genres such as [[Chiptune]], [[Electronic dance music|EDM]] and [[Drum and bass]].
